<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<!-- v3 -->
  <title>ホームページ制作代行 ご提案資料 | cafe nora</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --dk:    #0e0c09;
      --dk-m:  #1e1a14;
      --dk-l:  #2e2820;
      --gold:  #c8a96e;
      --gold-l:#e8d4a8;
      --cream: #faf6f0;
      --text:  #2c2018;
      --sub:   rgba(255,255,255,.78);
      --nav-h: 48px;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { height: 100%; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      background: #0e0c09;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100dvh;
    }

    /* ── スライドコンテナ ── */
    #stage {
      position: relative;
      width: min(100vw, calc((100vh - var(--nav-h)) * 16/9));
      aspect-ratio: 16/9;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .slide {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      padding: clamp(24px, 4%, 56px) clamp(28px, 6%, 80px);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      background: var(--dk);
      color: white;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(60px);
      transition: opacity .45s ease, transform .45s ease;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .slide.active {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: none;
      pointer-events: auto;
    }
    .slide.out {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(-60px);
    }

    /* ── 共通タイポグラフィ ── */
    .slide-label {
      font-size: clamp(.5rem, 1vw, .65rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .28em;
      color: var(--gold);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: .7em;
    }
    .slide-title {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3.2vw, 2.4rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-bottom: .6em;
    }
    .slide-title em {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--gold-l);
    }
    .slide-sub {
      font-size: clamp(.7rem, 1.3vw, .95rem);
      color: var(--sub);
      line-height: 1.9;
      margin-bottom: 1.2em;
    }
    .gold { color: var(--gold); }
    .gold-l { color: var(--gold-l); }

    /* ── 斜め装飾ライン ── */
    .slide::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; right: 0;
      width: 40%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, transparent 50%, rgba(200,169,110,.04) 50%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* ── 金線アクセント ── */
    .accent-line {
      width: clamp(32px, 4vw, 52px);
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 1.2em;
    }

    /* ── スライド1：表紙 ── */
    .s1 { background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 60%, #2a1f10 0%, var(--dk) 70%); justify-content: center; }
    .s1 .hero-label { font-size: clamp(.55rem, 1vw, .7rem); letter-spacing: .35em; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1.2em; }
    .s1 .main-title {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.8rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: .5em;
    }
    .s1 .main-title span { display: block; color: var(--gold-l); font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: .62em; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: .3em; letter-spacing: .08em; }
    .s1 .main-sub { font-size: clamp(.75rem, 1.4vw, 1rem); color: var(--sub); letter-spacing: .1em; margin-bottom: 2em; }
    .s1 .tag-row { display: flex; gap: clamp(6px,1vw,12px); flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .tag { background: rgba(200,169,110,.12); border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,.35); border-radius: 20px; padding: .3em .9em; font-size: clamp(.55rem,.9vw,.72rem); color: var(--gold-l); letter-spacing: .05em; }
    .s1 .logo-badge {
      position: absolute; top: clamp(16px,3%,28px); right: clamp(20px,4%,48px);
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: clamp(.6rem,1vw,.8rem);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.35);
      letter-spacing: .18em;
      text-align: right;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── スライド2：共感 ── */
    .s2 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a150e 0%, var(--dk) 100%); }
    .s2 .two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: clamp(20px,4vw,56px); align-items: center; }
    .check-list { list-style: none; }
    .check-list li { padding: .5em 0; font-size: clamp(.72rem,1.3vw,.95rem); color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .6em; }
    .check-list li::before { content: '▸'; color: var(--gold); font-size: .8em; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .callout { background: rgba(200,169,110,.1); border-left: 3px solid var(--gold); border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; padding: clamp(12px,2vw,20px) clamp(14px,2.5vw,24px); }
    .callout p { font-size: clamp(.7rem,1.2vw,.88rem); color: var(--sub); line-height: 1.9; }
    .callout strong { color: var(--gold-l); font-weight: 500; }

    /* ── スライド3：悩み ── */
    .s3 { background: var(--dk); }
    .pain-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: clamp(10px,1.5vw,18px); margin-top: .5em; }
    .pain-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: clamp(10px,1.5vw,18px) clamp(12px,2vw,22px);
    }
    .pain-card .q-mark { font-size: clamp(.65rem,1vw,.8rem); color: rgba(200,169,110,.6); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .15em; margin-bottom: .35em; }
    .pain-card p { font-size: clamp(.65rem,1.1vw,.82rem); color: rgba(255,255,255,.8); line-height: 1.7; }
    .pain-bottom { margin-top: clamp(12px,2vw,20px); background: rgba(200,169,110,.08); border-radius: 8px; padding: clamp(8px,1.5vw,14px) clamp(12px,2vw,20px); }
    .pain-bottom p { font-size: clamp(.65rem,1.1vw,.82rem); color: var(--sub); text-align: center; }
    .pain-bottom strong { color: var(--gold); }

    /* ── スライド4：メリット ── */
    .s4 { background: linear-gradient(160deg, #1a150e 0%, var(--dk) 80%); }
    .merit-list { list-style: none; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: clamp(8px,1.2vw,14px); }
    .merit-list li { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: .6em; font-size: clamp(.65rem,1.1vw,.83rem); color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); line-height: 1.7; }
    .merit-list li .icon { color: var(--gold); font-size: .9em; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: .15em; }
    .merit-note { margin-top: clamp(10px,2vw,20px); text-align: center; font-size: clamp(.6rem,.95vw,.75rem); color: rgba(200,169,110,.65); letter-spacing: .05em; font-style: italic; }

    /* ── スライド5：ページ内容 ── */
    .s5 { background: var(--dk); }
    .page-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: clamp(8px,1.2vw,14px); margin-top: .5em; }
    .page-card { background: rgba(200,169,110,.07); border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,.2); border-radius: 8px; padding: clamp(10px,1.5vw,16px); text-align: center; }
    .page-card .num { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(1rem,1.8vw,1.4rem); color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: .3em; }
    .page-card .name { font-size: clamp(.62rem,1vw,.78rem); color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: .3em; }
    .page-card .desc { font-size: clamp(.55rem,.85vw,.68rem); color: rgba(255,255,255,.45); line-height: 1.6; }
    .page-note { margin-top: clamp(8px,1.5vw,14px); text-align: center; font-size: clamp(.6rem,.9vw,.72rem); color: var(--sub); }

    /* ── スライド6：実績 ── */
    .s6 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a150e 0%, var(--dk) 100%); }
    .portfolio-frame {
      background: var(--dk-l);
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,.15);
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      margin-top: .5em;
    }
    .portfolio-bar { background: var(--dk-m); padding: clamp(6px,1vw,10px) clamp(12px,2vw,18px); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
    .dot { width: clamp(6px,1vw,8px); height: clamp(6px,1vw,8px); border-radius: 50%; }
    .dot.r { background: #ff5f57; } .dot.y { background: #ffbd2e; } .dot.g { background: #28c840; }
    .portfolio-screen { flex: 1; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: clamp(16px,3vw,32px); }
    .screen-placeholder {
      width: 100%; max-width: 480px;
      background: rgba(200,169,110,.06);
      border: 2px dashed rgba(200,169,110,.25);
      border-radius: 8px;
      aspect-ratio: 16/9;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: .5em;
    }
    .screen-placeholder .icon { font-size: clamp(1.2rem,2.5vw,2rem); color: rgba(200,169,110,.35); }
    .screen-placeholder p { font-size: clamp(.6rem,1vw,.75rem); color: rgba(255,255,255,.3); text-align: center; line-height: 1.6; }
    .s6-chips { display: flex; gap: clamp(6px,.8vw,10px); flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: .8em; }
    .s6-chip { background: rgba(200,169,110,.1); border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,.25); border-radius: 16px; padding: .25em .7em; font-size: clamp(.52rem,.85vw,.68rem); color: var(--gold-l); }

    /* ── スライド7：料金 ── */
    .s7 { background: var(--dk); }
    .plan-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: clamp(8px,1.2vw,14px); margin-top: .5em; flex: 1; }
    .plan-card { border-radius: 10px; padding: clamp(12px,2vw,20px); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .5em; }
    .plan-free { background: rgba(200,169,110,.08); border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,.3); }
    .plan-full { background: rgba(200,169,110,.15); border: 2px solid var(--gold); }
    .plan-support { background: rgba(255,255,255,.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1); }
    .plan-phase { font-size: clamp(.52rem,.85vw,.66rem); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .2em; color: var(--gold); text-transform: uppercase; }
    .plan-name { font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif; font-size: clamp(.8rem,1.4vw,1.05rem); font-weight: 600; color: white; }
    .plan-price { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(1.1rem,2vw,1.6rem); color: var(--gold-l); }
    .plan-price span { font-size: .45em; color: var(--sub); font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif; }
    .plan-list { list-style: none; flex: 1; }
    .plan-list li { font-size: clamp(.55rem,.88vw,.7rem); color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); padding: .25em 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05); line-height: 1.5; }
    .plan-list li::before { content: '—  '; color: rgba(200,169,110,.5); }
    .plan-badge { font-size: clamp(.5rem,.8vw,.62rem); background: var(--gold); color: var(--dk); font-weight: 700; padding: .2em .6em; border-radius: 10px; align-self: flex-start; }
    .plan-note { text-align: center; font-size: clamp(.55rem,.85vw,.68rem); color: rgba(200,169,110,.5); margin-top: .5em; letter-spacing: .04em; }

    /* ── スライド8：流れ ── */
    .s8 { background: linear-gradient(160deg, #1a150e 0%, var(--dk) 80%); }
    .steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: clamp(8px,1.2vw,14px); margin-top: .5em; flex: 1; }
    .step { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .4em; position: relative; }
    .step:not(:last-child)::after {
      content: '›'; position: absolute; right: clamp(-10px,-1vw,-6px); top: clamp(10px,1.8vw,16px);
      color: rgba(200,169,110,.4); font-size: clamp(.9rem,1.5vw,1.2rem);
    }
    .step-num { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(1.6rem,2.8vw,2.2rem); color: rgba(200,169,110,.25); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1; }
    .step-name { font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif; font-size: clamp(.7rem,1.2vw,.9rem); font-weight: 600; color: white; }
    .step-time { font-size: clamp(.55rem,.85vw,.68rem); color: var(--gold); font-weight: 500; }
    .step-desc { font-size: clamp(.58rem,.9vw,.72rem); color: rgba(255,255,255,.55); line-height: 1.7; margin-top: .2em; }
    .step-note { margin-top: clamp(10px,2vw,18px); background: rgba(200,169,110,.08); border-radius: 8px; padding: clamp(8px,1.2vw,14px); text-align: center; }
    .step-note p { font-size: clamp(.6rem,.95vw,.75rem); color: var(--sub); }
    .step-note strong { color: var(--gold-l); }

    /* ── スライド9：FAQ ── */
    .s9 { background: var(--dk); }
    .faq-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: clamp(8px,1.2vw,14px); margin-top: .5em; }
    .faq-item { background: rgba(255,255,255,.03); border-radius: 8px; padding: clamp(10px,1.5vw,16px); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06); }
    .faq-q { font-size: clamp(.63rem,1vw,.78rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold-l); margin-bottom: .4em; line-height: 1.5; }
    .faq-q::before { content: 'Q. '; color: var(--gold); }
    .faq-a { font-size: clamp(.6rem,.95vw,.73rem); color: rgba(255,255,255,.65); line-height: 1.75; }
    .faq-a::before { content: 'A. '; color: rgba(200,169,110,.5); font-weight: 500; }

    /* ── スライド10：まとめ ── */
    .s10 {
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 50%, #2a1f10 0%, var(--dk) 70%);
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .s10 .two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr; gap: clamp(20px,4vw,56px); align-items: center; }
    .summary-list { list-style: none; }
    .summary-list li { padding: .55em 0; font-size: clamp(.68rem,1.2vw,.88rem); color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,.12); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .65em; line-height: 1.6; }
    .summary-list li::before { content: '✦'; color: var(--gold); font-size: .65em; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .contact-box { background: rgba(200,169,110,.1); border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,.3); border-radius: 12px; padding: clamp(16px,2.5vw,28px); }
    .contact-box .cta-title { font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif; font-size: clamp(.85rem,1.5vw,1.15rem); font-weight: 600; color: white; margin-bottom: .6em; line-height: 1.5; }
    .contact-box .cta-note { font-size: clamp(.6rem,.95vw,.75rem); color: var(--sub); margin-bottom: 1em; line-height: 1.8; }
    .contact-line { padding: .45em 0; font-size: clamp(.6rem,.95vw,.75rem); color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06); }
    .contact-line strong { color: var(--gold-l); }
    .s10 .limit-badge { display: inline-block; background: var(--gold); color: var(--dk); font-weight: 700; font-size: clamp(.55rem,.85vw,.68rem); padding: .3em .8em; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 1em; letter-spacing: .04em; }

    /* ── ナビゲーション ── */
    #nav {
      height: var(--nav-h);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: clamp(8px,1.5vw,16px);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .nav-btn {
      background: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,.35);
      color: var(--gold);
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: .95rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      transition: all .2s;
    }
    .nav-btn:hover { background: rgba(200,169,110,.15); }
    .nav-btn:disabled { opacity: .3; cursor: default; }
    #counter { font-size: .75rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; min-width: 42px; text-align: center; }
    .dots { display: flex; gap: 6px; }
    .dot-nav { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(200,169,110,.25); cursor: pointer; transition: all .25s; border: none; padding: 0; }
    .dot-nav.active { background: var(--gold); transform: scale(1.25); }

    /* ── 縦向きオーバーレイ ── */
    #rotate-overlay {
      display: none;
      position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 9999;
      background: var(--dk);
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      text-align: center; gap: 1.2em;
    }
    #rotate-overlay .r-icon { font-size: 3rem; animation: rotate-hint 1.8s ease-in-out infinite; }
    @keyframes rotate-hint {
      0%,100% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
      40%      { transform: rotate(90deg); }
      60%      { transform: rotate(90deg); }
    }
    #rotate-overlay p { font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--gold-l); }
    #rotate-overlay small { font-size: .75rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.4); }
    @media screen and (orientation: portrait) {
      #rotate-overlay { display: flex; }
    }


    /* ── 印刷/PDF用（Ctrl+Pで使用） ── */
    @media print {
      body { overflow: visible; background: white; display: block; }
      #nav, #rotate-overlay { display: none !important; }
      #stage { width: 297mm; height: 167mm; position: relative; overflow: visible; }
      .slide { position: relative; opacity: 1 !important; transform: none !important; pointer-events: auto; page-break-after: always; height: 167mm; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="stage">

  <!-- ── スライド 1 ── -->
  <div class="slide s1 active">
    <div class="s1 logo-badge">cafe nora<br><span style="font-size:.75em;opacity:.6;letter-spacing:.1em;">ホームページ制作代行</span></div>
    <div class="accent-line"></div>
    <p class="hero-label">Web Design &amp; Production Service</p>
    <h1 class="main-title">
      <span>Your story deserves to be found.</span>
      あなたの活動を、<br>もっと多くの人へ。
    </h1>
    <p class="main-sub">ホームページ制作代行サービス — ご提案資料</p>
    <div class="tag-row">
      <span class="tag">個人事業主向け</span>
      <span class="tag">小規模店舗オーナー向け</span>
      <span class="tag">SNS運用中の方向け</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── スライド 2 ── -->
  <div class="slide s2">
    <div class="accent-line"></div>
    <p class="slide-label">Current Situation</p>
    <h2 class="slide-title">今、どこで活動を<em>伝えて</em>いますか？</h2>
    <div class="two-col">
      <ul class="check-list">
        <li>InstagramやXで投稿はしている</li>
        <li>口コミ・紹介でお客さんが来てくれている</li>
        <li>でも「次のステップ」がなかなか見えない</li>
        <li>もっと多くの人に知ってもらいたい、と感じている</li>
        <li>検索で見つけてもらえているか、正直わからない</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="callout">
        <p>SNSは活動を広める強力なツールです。<br>でも、<strong>「検索して見つけてもらう」</strong>には、ホームページが必要です。<br><br>SNSとホームページ、両方あることが<strong>最強の組み合わせ</strong>です。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── スライド 3 ── -->
  <div class="slide s3">
    <div class="accent-line"></div>
    <p class="slide-label">Pain Points</p>
    <h2 class="slide-title">告知は<em>SNSだけ</em>…それで十分ですか？</h2>
    <div class="pain-grid">
      <div class="pain-card">
        <p class="q-mark">QUESTION 01</p>
        <p>営業日・場所・サービス内容、どこで確認できますか？<br>SNSは古い情報が流れてしまいます。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card">
        <p class="q-mark">QUESTION 02</p>
        <p>問い合わせはDMだけですか？<br>見逃しや返信漏れは起きていませんか？</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card">
        <p class="q-mark">QUESTION 03</p>
        <p>あなたの世界観・雰囲気、写真と一言だけで<br>伝わっていると思いますか？</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card">
        <p class="q-mark">QUESTION 04</p>
